snippet.title: Thief: The Black Parade - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Download The Black Parade now here: https://www.ttlg.com/forums/showthread.php?t=152429
You can also download it from ModDB: https://www.moddb.com/mods/thief-the-black-parade

The Black Parade is an unofficial FREE expansion for Thief Gold with 10 new missions, 4 new tools, 30 minutes of gorgeous cutscenes and more!
